Team > Steve Betts
 
 




			Steve Betts		
 
 





Steve a native of Creston, Iowa and his wife Sheri, live in the Northwest Iowa community of LeMars. His career has included fertilizer positions with Honeywell, United Suppliers and most recently with Ag Partners. He has spent more than 25 years in the fertilizer industry with primary focus on fertilizer and risk management.
Steve is a graduate of Florida Southern College with and MBA in business administration.
Steve enjoys recreational activities such as golf, running, and fishing and is an avid supporter of the Iowa State University Cyclones. The Betts Family includes son Chris and daughter-in-law Lauren.
 
 

MPower Rewards 

In addition to already competitive pricing, MPOWER eligible products pay you back MPOWER Rewards. 

After all the book work is complete to calculate the savings FNA Members have generated through volume, logistics, currency risk, management and marketing, a cash reward is determined and made available to FNA Members.


The MPOWER Rewards system makes room for more value creation as the savings in business efficiencies are paid back to the Members. 


MPOWER Rewards means more money in your pocket.

