W.B. Mason is the largest privately held office products dealer in the United States and is headquartered in Brockton, Massachusetts. The company was founded in 1898 and has been family owned ever since. W.B. Mason has over 60 distribution centers across the United States. The company has more than 3,600 employees, including 1200 sales representatives. W.B. Mason leases 1100 delivery trucks from Ryder, and services more than 300,000 businesses,[5][6]. W.B. Mason is the largest purchaser of goods from Essendant.[7][8]



